{"type": "article", "id": 43105, "title": "伪装成耳机的风扇，方便但似乎有点中二｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-07-17T23:40:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 16308, "name": "Thanko"}, {"id": 34472, "name": "BuzziSpace"}, {"id": 42431, "name": "Huskee"}, {"id": 42432, "name": "13&9 Design"}, {"id": 42433, "name": "Niv Rozenberg"}, {"id": 42434, "name": "Julia Jamrozik"}, {"id": 42435, "name": "Coryn Kempster"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 95, "image": "img/article/article_show/201707180739557CtG0XzLhAKjNYlV.png", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Huskee Cup by Huskee</h3><p>据统计，每年有超过 135 万吨的咖啡豆壳被当作垃圾丢弃，这在澳大利亚的一群咖啡爱好者看来，是极大的浪费。为此，他们成立了一个名为 Huskee 的公司，致力于开发豆壳加工而成的产品。虽然外观上和陶瓷咖啡杯并没有太大差异，这套 Huskee Cup 胜在它的抗裂性以及号称更好的保温功能。杯子表面的纹路不仅能防止烫伤，清洁后也能更好地排掉液体。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1366930566/huskeecup-waste-made-beautiful\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价从 45 澳元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185234vke4a8BTosYjNn9V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.511765\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185234eT9JGUBNW7ws2moy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.514706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185234MBGNRFTHmovx6YJb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.510294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185234GtW5xzm3hegCk6Bo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.364706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Headphone Cooler by Thanko</h3><p>随着气温升高，便携式小风扇又重新得到青睐。最近，日本家电公司 <a href=\"http://www.thanko.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thanko</a> 就推出了一款伪装成耳机的 USB 风扇，免去了时刻需要举着设备的烦恼。耳机风扇仅重 159 克，出风口位于耳机的边缘，刚好可以将风送往脖子和脸颊，也可以根据需要调整角度。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.thanko.jp/shopdetail/000000002815\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 2980 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017071718525124WJbz5ovpHBeQgw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.550000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185251lecb6wtCRTkmPG5z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185252mx82o7LqXByhADna.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.475000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>BuzziPleat by 13&amp;9 Design</h3><p>我们此前曾介绍过比利时家具设计公司 <a href=\"http://buzzi.space/\" rel=\"nofollow\">BuzziSpace</a> 推出的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/29891.html\">吸音产品</a>，旗下的最新产品是他们与奥地利设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.13and9design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">13&amp;9 Design</a> 联手打造的 <a href=\"http://buzzi.space/buzzipleat/\" rel=\"nofollow\">BuzziPleat</a>。13&amp;9 借鉴了在服饰设计中的传统工艺，这些褶皱很容易让人联想到经典的拉夫领。BuzziPleat 既可以单独使用，也能在正中央加入灯泡，变成一盏吊灯。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185308DlXdqO1vWjZrUt3Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185308WJztNbYCufBGs0jI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185308VaXBRqKFbmSYCjZE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.808594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Yu Hua Tailor by Jay Liu</h3><p>玉桦裁缝是新加坡裁缝师李玉兰的个人品牌，设计师 <a href=\"https://www.jay-l.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jay Liu</a> 为她打造的品牌形象走的是极简又富有精致感的路线。几乎纯白的名片正中央压印了品牌名，左右两边延长的线头意味着名片可以直接当作服饰的标签。类似的压印和缝线同样出现在配套的办公用品上，Liu 还特意参考了传统的白衬衫，在信封背面加入了“袖口”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185322tY4FDaXiWOj9Eg3G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185322XSzqgATHrnjopmKx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017071718532247RCNIG8xp1M6EAz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185322CLrAWf7IZuBOephD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185323TauovV6brNdtpAY1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Boswijck by Niv Rozenberg</h3><p>如果你对纽约布鲁克林的建筑感兴趣，不妨来看看以色列摄影师 <a href=\"http://nivrozenberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Niv Rozenberg</a> 创作的 <a href=\"http://nivrozenberg.com/?p=613\" rel=\"nofollow\">Boswijck</a> 系列。Boswijck 指的是布鲁克林的布什维克（Bushwick）街区，也是 Rozenberg 的现居地。当地多元的建筑风格启发他将那些特别的建筑独立出来，并用它们的颜色去填充画面的背景，整套作品就像是对建筑进行了扁平化的处理，非常有趣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185347IAJlVWvbqMZhpyEO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185346SGP9LnT16FAgNIXB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185346a7RhDoYycUsqN6vG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185347SbCD0ZEHvUKm23p6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707171853483KfvcF2gtb47PGuS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Vertical Line Garden by Julia Jamrozik &amp; Coryn Kempster</h3><p>在今年的魁北克<a href=\"http://www.refordgardens.com/english/\" rel=\"nofollow\">国际花园节</a>上，加拿大设计师 Julia Jamrozik 和 Coryn Kempster 组成的<a href=\"http://www.ck-jj.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">双人艺术组合</a>用色彩缤纷的胶带打造了一个名为 Vertical Line Garden 的装置。这些平时用来封锁场地的胶带从白色的框架上垂下，时不时随风飘荡，吸引着好奇的路人走近，探索这个并不传统的花园。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185432qwaNd76eBQhjz9JL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185433dmOBKD5MA0XkPYpr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185433Na1fhRsCA0DmU53x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170717185433QeRuFkmNEWOfTi8V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}